Any call to `stop()` _must_ be preceded by a call to `start()`, and `start()` must be preceded by a call to `prepare()`.

In other words,

    private void setupMediaRecorder()
    {
        mediaRecorder= new MediaRecorder();
        ...
        mediaRecorder.prepare();
    }

    private void startRecording()
    {
        mediaRecorder.start();
    }

